1) When using the generator, do not touch myuserhook.h and myuserhook.cpp
2) Change the polariztion and spinningparticleID at the macro definiation of EventGen.cc
3) Select the physics topology in InputPhysicsCard/XXXX.cmnd

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Before compile, specify your root library in Makefile.inc
Or you can replace the Makefile.inc with your own version in your Pythia/Examples/
To compile use --bash$ make EventGen
To Run use     --bash$ ./EventGen InputPhysicsCard/XXXX.cmnd

